        Ghana Tax Templates
        VAT Act 1151 (effective January 2026)

        Tax Structure:
        - VAT: 15%
        - NHIL: 2.5% (National Health Insurance Levy) - Input deductible
        - GETFund: 2.5% (Ghana Education Trust Fund) - Input deductible
        - Total effective rate: 20%

        COVID-19 Levy: ABOLISHED
        NHIL and GETFund: Now re-coupled to VAT base (input deductible)
        -->

